To create modules-$VERSION.sfs:
	* turn off discrete graphics
	* load an Ubuntu Live CD
	* install VirtualBox
	* install VirtualBox Guest Additions:
		- mount VBoxGuestAdditions.iso, run VBoxLinuxAdditions.run
	* cp -a /lib/{firmware,modules}
	* [x86] http://wireless.kernel.org/en/users/Drivers/b43 -> list of firmware -> b43legacy
	* [x86] copy b43legacy to /lib/modules/firmware/
	* [x64] install ZFS:
		- apt-add-repository ppa:zfs-native/stable && apt-get update && apt-get install ubuntu-zfs
		- save userspace files to github.com/sigaev/zfs
	* ln -s /cdrom/secret /lib/modules/
	* install NVidia drivers:
		- Ctrl-Alt-F1, service lightdm stop, run NVIDIA-Linux-$VERSION.run
		- save userspace files to github.com/sigaev/nvidia
	* mksquashfs /lib/modules modules-$VERSION.sfs -comp xz
